Interface AbstractRepository.Listener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the entity type
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractRepository<ID,​T>
    public static interface AbstractRepository.Listener<T>
    An interface that should be implemented by the clients interested in repository events.
